">お</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いつくために、まるで半分<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">馳</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">か</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>けた。みんな急いで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">着物</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きもの</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をぬいで、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">淵</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">岸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に立つと、<span rend="sesame_dot" rendition="em">しゅっこ</span>が云った。<lb />
